summary: I am an enthusiastic, hard working and responsible person with extensive international experience. My specialties include multi-cultural environments and communication, business development, market analysis, strategy development and I am an expert in Supply Chain and Logistics Management. I offer an extensive network in strategic sectors such as Agriculture, Renewable Energy, Logistics and Trade Promotion. I consider myself a strong and creative bridge builder between these different specialities, experiences, sectors and cultures.
